{"tid":243683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兼職入行指南","createTime":"2017-05-14T22:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T17:05:56.000Z","uid":112767,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed0bea4b777457380b3d2a03e618a0bb8641f03","tid":243683,"uid":112767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T22:05:46.000Z","msg":"利申：學生一名，已有數十載不同工作經驗背景，純分享心得<br />\n<br />\n首先，大型快餐連鎖集團<br />\n           Ex m記 kfc&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n好處：工作時間彈性，基本上想番咩更都有(長期缺人)，       <br />\n           只要你係人都請，而且入面龍蛇混雜，見識可能會<br />\n           多左(可能)<br />\n<br />\n壞處：人工低到喊，普遍3x到40(btw如果識人有補鐘比<br />\n           你上到5x到6x一個鐘，大前提要同經理熟)，放飯<br />\n           冇錢，冇小休，長期有客(忙)，基本上玩唔到手<br />\n           機，人龍一長手腳慢比客屌<br />\n<br />\n總括   (山窮水盡也可屌)<br />\n<br />\n其次，普通餐飲<br />\n            Ex  茶記 日西式餐廳&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n好處:   通常包三餐，如果做廚房應該冇王管(偷食 蛇等)<br />\n            工作時間都彈性，人情味夠，通常忙午晚時段，<br />\n            其餘時間可hea，人工普遍4x至5x，<br />\n<br />\n壞處： 六日會好chur，工作性質偏辛苦，要不停出菜<br />\n            清潔等，放題辛苦程度就更上一層樓，工作性質<br />\n            單一，悶<br />\n            <br />\n總括    (選擇一間合適地區嘅餐廳)<br />\n<br />\n再者，銷售行業<br />\n           Ex it u記&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n好處：人工比上述高，公價50，性質偏hea，跟客 摺衫<br />\n           等，通常part time唔使追數，容易識靚囡，同年<br />\n           紀較多，可以次下水等<br />\n<br />\n壞處：硬性規定一次比月更表，每星期先通知你番咩更<br />\n           ，未必齊更，通常D full time都閪(btw人品)，同<br />\n            埋見工睇樣，唔可以太毒 太㭍，要有自信 要識<br />\n            吹<br />\n<br />\n總括    (可以一試)<br />\n<br />\n然後，補習行業<br />\n           Ex 補習杜<br />\n<br />\n好處：人工都有5x至6x，教下D小學雞都幾過癮，而且<br />\n           較舒服，如果教極唔識可以直接比答案，D細路<br />\n           仲開心過你<br />\n<br />\n壞處：工時少，通常都係番4點到7點到，D細路唔聽話<br />\n           都幾勞氣，暫冇其他<br />\n<br />\n總括     (抵玩)<br />\n<br />\n繼而，炒散<br />\n            Ex 飲食 洒店<br />\n<br />\n好處：人工高，通常6x up，想番就搵蛇頭，適合自由人<br />\n            但前提要有工作經驗，<br />\n<br />\n壞處：偏辛苦，工作未必穩定，通常要 皮鞋 西褲 黑頭，<br />\n            同埋要熟手<br />\n<br />\n總括    (還可以)<br />\n<br />\n暫時分享咁多，如果想問番 狗會 倉務 洒店 或其他工種，<br />\n 可以留言，遲下再分享，歡迎大家討論"},{"pid":"05f9d6d2ac7c74b37b155ad5d094f9f676d1fc21","tid":243683,"uid":62070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T22:09:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b76d327e61614be85ff9df9098c828df6f337184","tid":243683,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T22:16:46.000Z","msg":"有冇返過打字員"},{"pid":"9ab3b4ecbc7c029c6fe58f1087f86f15d715a65b","tid":243683,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T22:29:58.000Z","msg":"補習當然做私補，坐一陣又舊幾，由其理科，叫佢做下數又一day<br />\n巴打無做過promotion？嗰啲先好揾，有時揾囡囡派下花又120/hr"},{"pid":"d5dd0c9e354ee21cf0196c2b02d39e0da9295d53","tid":243683,"uid":57643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T22:49:39.000Z","msg":"想知有咩工係狗也不屌"},{"pid":"ade2df8bf423c223bba015204926907bc3b5b8de","tid":243683,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T22:57:06.000Z","msg":"試過扮吉祥物（冬天）<br />\n100/H<br />\n4小時<br />\n鳩下鳩下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834c010200805fca3f352d171534bd36ae00286e","tid":243683,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T22:58:09.000Z","msg":"炒散其實唔洗工作經驗<br />\n家下好缺人咩人都請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55a376fae7ffb6002fbd9a6fbd8f09ee61b2bc5","tid":243683,"uid":112767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:17:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下推廣員或者商場活動之類請班人黎hea<br />\n呢啲工係邊搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常熟人介紹，但暑假都請5少呢d，例如會展 某商店果d promoter"},{"pid":"3c92de152adecc3dd82ab706ace13a018d5e0743","tid":243683,"uid":112767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇返過打字員</blockquote><br />\n有，通常test你打字快5快，同埋一個字，悶"},{"pid":"97ef4e4ba6ffec6d346f7847667f61a5890e7d85","tid":243683,"uid":112767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補習當然做私補，坐一陣又舊幾，由其理科，叫佢做下數又一day<br />\n巴打無做過promotion？嗰啲先好揾，有時揾囡囡派下花又120/hr</blockquote><br />\n都有做過，但時薪得50"},{"pid":"1eee1079753d8597e169d56d9c6f268487f99353","tid":243683,"uid":112767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:25:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知有咩工係狗也不屌</blockquote><br />\n通常看自已可接受範圍，ex 馬會60一個鐘。但我覺得真系垃到一個點，但有人都會做"},{"pid":"3cdba0d8e75a54e44c8610b10daf5cc669fc36e0","tid":243683,"uid":112767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過扮吉祥物（冬天）<br />\n100/H<br />\n4小時<br />\n鳩下鳩下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同感，我試過500扮4小時，做完好像沖左幾次凉"},{"pid":"31325ee4e766535e5fb89a94d17f008bc1e66d0c","tid":243683,"uid":112767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:28:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒散其實唔洗工作經驗<br />\n家下好缺人咩人都請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高人工果d通常要，不夠宜家真系好缺人"},{"pid":"9306f4c40ef36e728846742c4a25702001a801d8","tid":243683,"uid":48633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想知有咩工係狗也不屌</blockquote><br />\n通常看自已可接受範圍，ex 馬會60一個鐘。但我覺得真系垃到一個點，但有人都會做</blockquote><br />\n點樣垃圾法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f8d9ce45454b6be16630b0329d151b87613896","tid":243683,"uid":60156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過扮吉祥物（冬天）<br />\n100/H<br />\n4小時<br />\n鳩下鳩下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同感，我試過500扮4小時，做完好像沖左幾次凉</blockquote><br />\n你肯定比人呃...<br />\n我之前公司負責搵promoter, 果d位最少出到200-250一小時先有人做。條友入左去15分鐘件衫已經濕哂，入面把風扇有等於無..做完同焗桑拿係無分別"},{"pid":"7d672250cdd692ae1a621b1fe571f66582287df7","tid":243683,"uid":112767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:05:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想知有咩工係狗也不屌</blockquote><br />\n通常看自已可接受範圍，ex 馬會60一個鐘。但我覺得真系垃到一個點，但有人都會做</blockquote><br />\n點樣垃圾法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nD阿伯閪到一個點，壓力又大"},{"pid":"99445b6ed9b5f7a6edd4dc38225d9f7ef1ecc197","tid":243683,"uid":110282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:45:18.000Z","msg":"如果想搵份工識下人（男女均可），有沒推介？"},{"pid":"84ebbc6ba7c91dcc47ce342858fd1cbbec00f4f4","tid":243683,"uid":125931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c92de152adecc3dd82ab706ace13a018d5e0743","tid":243683,"uid":112767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇返過打字員</blockquote><br />\n有，通常test你打字快5快，同埋一個字，悶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T17:05:56.000Z","msg":"有冇介紹 悶我唔太怕 但我只可兼職"}]}